## Quick Reference Card

### Emergency OSINT Workflow

**1. Starting Point**
   ↓
**2. Search Engine** (Google, operators)
   ↓
**3. Social Media** (Namechk for username)
   ↓
**4. Email Discovery** (Hunter.io)
   ↓
**5. Breach Check** (Have I Been Pwned → DeHashed)
   ↓
**6. Image Analysis** (Google/Yandex reverse search)
   ↓
**7. Location** (Maps, Street View, EXIF)
   ↓
**8. Cross-Reference** (Find patterns, connections)
   ↓
**9. Document** (Screenshots, notes, timeline)
   ↓
**10. Report** (Compile findings)
